    answer: "Most cards offer multiple redemption options: <strong>statement credits</strong> (most common), <strong>direct deposit</strong> to bank accounts, <strong>check by mail</strong>, or <strong>gift cards</strong> (sometimes at bonus value). Statement credits and direct deposits typically offer the best value. Avoid redeeming for merchandise, which often gives worse value."
  },
